 <i> l'amore, l'amore.</i>             

795
00:43:46,990 --> 00:43:48,557
     [SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]      

796
00:43:48,559 --> 00:43:50,559
You like-a vino, Joe?           

797
00:43:50,561 --> 00:43:52,261
                     Ah, no,    
