01:13:49,290 --> 01:13:51,157
          Wildcat six.          
      This is Wildcat two.      

1405
01:13:51,159 --> 01:13:53,193
      Fire mission. Over.       
      Fire mission point.       

1406
01:13:53,195 --> 01:13:54,394
      [ARTILLERY WHIZZING]      

