01:13:57,364 --> 01:14:00,233
 Fire mission point, Fox-Able-  
    Easy-Baker-Mike-Charlie,    

1408
01:14:00,235 --> 01:14:03,471
 and point, King-Sugar-Charlie- 
         Love-Able-How.         

